e%2F078fbad0-bdf2-11ef-b3ff-2979052719d0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc89xdd07585o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20widely%20advertised%20event%20saw%20large%20numbers%20of%20children%20show%20up%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20deadly%20crush.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc89xdd07585o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc89xdd07585o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc89xdd07585o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBJP's%20Bid%20To%20Distract%20From%20Ambedkar%20Row%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20On%20Parliament%20Tussle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20clarifying%20the%20party's%20stance%20on%20the%20tussle%20that%20took%20place%20at%20the%20Parliament%20complex%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20chaos%20was%20engineered%20to%20distract%20from%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20'fashion'%20remarks%20on%20BR%20Ambedkar%20that%20ignited%20a%20massive%20row%20between%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20front%20of%20him%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20distract%20from%20the%20issues%20since%20the%20Parliament%20session%20began%20and%20the%20Congress%20has%20always%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20party's%20thought%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-constitutional%20and%20anti-Ambedkar%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20erase%20Ambedkar's%20memory%20and%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Home%20Minister%20exposed%20this%20mindset%20(with%20his%20remarks).%20We%20called%20for%20an%20apology%20and%20a%20resignation%2C%20which%20did%20not%20happen.%20Today%2C%20they%20began%20a%20new%20distraction.%20Opposition%20MPs%20were%20heading%20to%20Parliament%20House%20from%20Ambdekar%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E's%20statue%20and%20BJP%20MPs%20were%20standing%20near%20the%20stairs%20with%20sticks%20in%20their%20hands%2C%20refusing%20to%20let%20us%20go%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20he%20(Mr%20Shah)%20has%20insulted%20Ambedkar%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20should%20apologise%20and%20resign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20%C2%A0Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20also%20addressed%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20said%20the%20party%20condemns%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20mindset%20they%20portray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20refused%20to%20accept%20he%20had%20done%20anything%20wrong.%20We%20asked%20for%20his%20resignation%20and%2C%20failing%20that%2C%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20sack%20him.%20We%20realised%20neither%20of%20these%20things%20was%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20so%20leaders%20of%20our%20party%2C%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20protested.%20But%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20divert%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%20claimed%20BJP%20MPs%20tried%20to%20prevent%20legislators%20from%20his%20party%20from%20entering%20Parliament%20and%20attacked%20them.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20also%20pushed%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20ground%20after%20losing%20balance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20doing%20this%2C%20they%20are%20alleging%20we%20pushed%20people%20and%20caused%20injuries.%20They%20were%20sitting%20and%20making%20fun%20of%20us.%20There%20were%20many%20woman%20MPs%20with%20us%20too...%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20this.%20The%20movement%20(against%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20Ambedkar)%20will%20become%20a%20national%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComplaint%2C%20Counter-Complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20alleged%20that%20members%20from%20the%20opposite%20side%20attacked%20and%20pushed%20their%20MPs%20when%20legislators%20from%20the%20Opposition%20party%20were%20entering%20Parliament%20House%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%20While%20the%20Congress%20was%20protesting%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20organised%20a%20counter-protest%20against%20the%20Opposition%20party%2C%20alleging%20it%20had%20disrespected%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20injured%20two%20of%20its%20MPs%2C%20Pratap%20Sarangi%20and%20Mukesh%20Rajput.%20The%20BJP%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20pushed%20Mr%20Rajput%2C%20who%20fell%20on%20Mr%20Sarangi.%20Both%20MPs%20were%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20with%20injuries%20and%20the%20BJP%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Parliament%20Street%20police%20station%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Nagaland%20MP%20Pahangnon%20Konyak%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Gandhi%20of%20misbehaving%20with%20her%20when%20she%20and%20her%20colleagues%20were%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20protest%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20same%20police%20station%20alleging%20BJP%20leaders%20pushed%20Mr%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEighty-four-year-old%20Dalit%20leader%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20pushed%20and%20misbehaved%20with.%20We%20have%20come%20here%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20this%20act%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20MP%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%20Remarks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%20during%20a%20debate%20commemorating%2075%20years%2