20Ukraine%20envoy%20said%20this%20week%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Russian%20general%20was%20outside%20the%20rules%20of%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20also%20criticized%20Biden's%20decision%20to%20allow%20strikes%20on%20Russia%20using%20US-supplied%20missiles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20worrying%20sign%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%20has%20signaled%20its%20disapproval%20of%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Russian%20soil%2C%20including%20long-range%20strikes%20and%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20top%20general%20in%20Moscow%20using%20a%20scooter%20bomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20envoy%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20retired%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Keith%20Kellogg%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-chemical-weapons-head-killed-in-bomb-explosion-in-moscow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20claimed%20killing%20of%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Igor%20Kirillov%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20was%20contrary%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirillov%2C%20who%20headed%20up%20Russia's%20chemical%2C%20nuclear%2C%20and%20biological%20protection%20troops%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20bomb%20planted%20on%20a%20scooter%20in%20Moscow%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ukraine%20has%20claimed%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Fox%20Business%2C%20Kellogg%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20rules%20of%20warfare%20and%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20you%20just%20kind%20of%20don't%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20killing%20flag%20officers%2C%20general%20officers%2C%20admirals%20or%20generals%20in%20their%20hometown%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20like%20you've%20extended%20it%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20really%20smart%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20said%20it%20had%20arrested%20a%20man%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20killing%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20suspected%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bterroris