press%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734612617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116475143%2Cimgsize-3933937.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fwindows-shattered-and-dismantled-incensed-over-locked-doors-passengers-vandalise-antyodaya-express-train-in-uttar-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F116475093.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angry%20passengers%20vandalized%20the%20Antyodaya%20Express%20at%20Basti%20station.%20They%20broke%20a%20window%20and%20grill%20to%20enter%20the%20locked%20train.%20The%20train%20was%20overcrowded.%20Passengers%20inside%20had%20locked%20the%20doors%20to%20prevent%20more%20boarding.%20RPF%20is%20investigating%20the%20incident.%20They%20are%20using%20video%20footage%20to%20identify%20the%20vandals.%20No%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ARVIND%20CHAUHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20R%20Ashwin%3A%20A%20Hero%20No%20One%20Was%20Fighting%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Foffrg89_r-ashwin_625x300_19_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20terms%20in%20sporting%20parlance%20that%20no%20athlete%20wants%20to%20see%20written%20alongside%20his%20or%20her%20name.%20The%20one%20that%20perhaps%20hurts%20the%20most%20is%20%E2%80%98bench-warmer'.%20So%20when%20it%20is%20used%2C%20quite%20regularly%2C%20for%20someone%20who%20is%2038%20and%20running%20out%20of%20time%20and%20also%20the%20only%20player%20in%20Test%20cricket%20history%20who%20has%20scored%20more%20than%20five%20Test%20centuries%20(six)%20and%20taken%20500%20wickets%20or%20more%20(537)%2C%20it%20is%20bound%20to%20pinch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20R.%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20won%20a%20world%20record-equalling%2011th%20Man%20of%20the%20Series%20award%20in%20the%20Test%20series%20with%20Bangladesh%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20decided%20to%20suddenly%20announce%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%20(a%20la%20MS%20Dhoni%20exactly%20ten%20years%20ago)%2C%20was%20it%20really%20shocking%3F%20Maybe%2C%20but%20not%20if%20you%20scratch%20the%20surface.%20The%20signs%20were%20there%20for%20a%20while.%20He%20just%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20bench%20warmer%20anymore.%20Bringing%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20his%20own%20terms%20was%20the%20only%20logical%20step%20forward.%20Kudos%20to%20him%20for%20being%20such%20a%20gentleman%2C%20even%20while%20taking%20the%20toughest%20call%20of%20them%20all.%20But%20that's%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20for%20you%E2%80%94he%20may%20wear%20his%20heart%20on%20his%20sleeve%2C%20but%20he'll%20never%20lose%20his%20poise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Signs%20Were%20There%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20cricket%20pundit%20to%20read%20and%20interpret%20the%20signs%20that%20indicate%20change%20is%20in%20the%20air.%20As%20Ashwin%20himself%20said%2C%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma%20sitting%20next%20to%20him%3A%20We%20are%20the%20last%20bunch%20of%20OGs.%E2%80%9D%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20trying%20out%20new%20or%20less%20experienced%20players%20on%20overseas%20tours%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20SENA%20countries%2C%20was%20unheard%20of%20for%20Indian%20teams.%20But%20things%20are%20changing.%20The%20ongoing%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20in%20fact%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20captures%20the%20essence%20of%20that%20change.%20Harshit%20Rana%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Reddy%20made%20their%20Test%20debuts%20in%20the%20very%20first%20match%20of%20the%20series%2C%20and%20Washington%20Sundar%20(who%20called%20Ashwin%20a%20mentor)%2C%20was%20picked%20ahead%20of%20Ashwin.%20If%20this%20was%20the%20case%20after%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20Tests%2C%20the%20message%20would%20have%20been%20a%20different%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20that%20went%20out%20here%2C%20though%2C%20was%20that%20Washy%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20better%20bet%E2%80%94in%20terms%20of%20an%20off-spinner%20who%20can%20bat%E2%80%94than%20Ashwin%20in%20Aussie%20conditions.%20Australia%20is%20a%20venue%20where%20all%20teams%20like%20to%20bat%20deep.%20Apart%20from%20the%20537%20Test%20wickets%20that%20Ashwin%20has%20(536%20before%20his%20last%20Test%20in%20Adelaide)%2C%20he%20also%20has%20six%20Test%20tons%20and%20is%20widely%20known%20as%20someone%20who%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20pride%20in%20his%20batting%20and%20can%20wield%20a%20willow%20effectively.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20began%20his%20career%20in%20age-group%20cricket%20as%20an%20opening%20batsman.%20But%20the%20management%2C%20helmed%20by%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20is%20famous%20for%20his%20no-nonsense%20and%20%E2%80%9Cteam%20first%E2%80%9D%20approach%2C%20is%20very%20clearly%20looking%20ahead%20and%20planning%20for%20the%20future.%20They%20want%20to%20throw%20the%20young%20guns%20into%20the%20deep%20end%2C%20forging%20them%20in%20the%20fire%20of%20unfriendly%20conditions.%20And%20you%20can't%20do%20that%20without%20keeping%20the%20%E2%80%98OGs'%20at%20the%20shallow%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMixed%20Signals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20sure%20that%20Ashwin%2C%20being%20the%20intelligent%20cricketer%20that%20he%20is%2C%20must%20understand%20that.%20But%20what%20would%20have%20frustrated%20him%20perhaps%20are%20the%20mixed%20signals.%20For%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20he%20didn't%20know%20whether%20he%20was%20in%20the%20scheme%20of%20things%20or%20not.%20It's%20been%20like%20this%20in%20the%20shorter%20formats%20of%20the%20game%20for%20a%20while%E2%80%94the%20last%20ODI%20he%20played%20was%20against%20Australia%20in%20Chennai%20in%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20last%20T20I%20he%20played%20was%20way%20back%20in%20November%202022%20in%20the%2010-wicket%20semi-final%20loss%20vs%20England%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20career%20though%2C%20Ashwin%20continued%20to%20reinvent%20himself%2C%20knowing%20fully%20well%20that%20it%20was%20the%20brand%20of%20cricket%20he%20played%20that%20would%20keep%20him%20relevant.%20He%20wasn't%20scared%20of%20trying%20new%20things%E2%80%94new%20run-ups%2C%20new%20delivery%20angles%2C%20perfecting%20his%20variation%20of%20the%20carrom%20ball%3B%20he%20became%20a%20true%20match-winner.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20the%20increasing%20frequency%20of%20him%20not%20being%20certain%20of%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Test%20playing%20XI%20was%20clearly%20the%20last%20straw%20for%20a%20man%20who%20prides%20himself%20on%20coming%20up%20with%20out-of-the-box%20solutions%20to%20fox%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%2C%20as%20reports%20suggest%2C%20he%20has%20been%20prepared%20to%20hang%20up%20his%20boots%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20his%20friends%20thought%20he%20was%20feeling%20low%20for%20a%20while%20and%20his%20family%20too%20had%20been%20informed%20that%20retirement%20might%20be%20on%20the%20horizon.%20Rohit%20himself%20talked%20about%20how%20Ashwin's%20retirement%20talks%20had%20surfaced%20during%20the%20Perth%20Test%20and%20how%20he%20had%20convinced%20the%20veteran%20off-spinner%20to%20stay%20on.%20Ashwin%20was%20picked%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Adelaide%20Test%2C%20where%20he%20bowled%2018%20overs%20in%20Australia's%20first%20innings%20and%20took%201%2F53.%20India%20lost%20by%2010%20wickets.%20In%20the%20next%20match%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Ashwin%20had%20to%20make%20way%20for%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20who%20didn't%20take%20a%20wicket%2C%20but%20scored%2077%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India's%20top%20order%20had%20not%20been%20firing%20on%20all%20cylinders.%20That%2C%20for%20Ashwin%2C%20was%20it.%20He%20knew%20he%20couldn't%20wait%20longer%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20decide%20his%20own%20fate.%20The%20last%20thing%20any%20champion%20athlete%20wants%20is%20to%20be%20pushed%20out.%20Will%20we%20see%20another%20retirement%20or%20two%20after%20this%20series%20is%20over%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20cricketer%20worth%20his%20or%20her%20salt%20will%20take%20the%20call%20to%20end%20their%20international%20career%20unless%20they%20are%20sure%20the%20time%20has%20come%E2%80%94or%2C%20they%20have%20been%20told%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20chances%20of%20any%20consistent%20participation%20in%20the%20future%20are%20up%20in%20the%20air.%20In%20Ashwin's%20case%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20it%20was%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%20There%20must%20have%20been%20another%20chat%20(just%20like%20the%20one%20during%20the%20Perth%20Test)%20and%20he%20would%20have%20realised%20that%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall.%20Did%20he%20deserve%20a%20better%20exit%3F%20Yes%2C%20most%20definitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Ashwin%20Needed%20To%20Get%20Away%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Ashwin%20took%20the%20call%20with%20two%20full%20Tests%20left%20to%20play%20and%20the%20series%20well%20and%20truly%20in%20the%20balance%20at%201-1%20is%20indication%20enough%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20get%20away%20from%20it%20all.%20Away%20from%20the%20media%2C%20away%20from%20the%20team%20environment%2C%20away%20from%20fans%2C%20away%20from%20the%20game%20he%20has%20lived%20and%20breathed%20since%20he%20was%20a%20teenager.%20The%20last%20Test%20of%20the%20series%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Sydney%20in%20the%20new%20year%E2%80%94a%20venue%20where%20India%20could%20field%20two%20spinners.%20But%20clearly%2C%20Ashwin%20didn't%20have%20the%20assurance%20he%20needed%20that%20he%20would%20be%20among%20the%20two%20first-choice%20spinners%20at%20the%20SCG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20those%20who%20might%20feel%20that%20Ashwin's%20decision%20was%20a%20hasty%20one.%20But%20remember%2C%20he%20is%20the%20same%20man%20who%20staunchly%20stuck%20to%20his%20strategy%20of%20running%20out%20batters%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end%20when%20they%20backed%20up%20too%20much%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20brickbats.%20He%20was%20never%20afraid%20to%20take%20the%20unpopular%20or%20uncommon%20route%2C%20as%20long%20as%20he%20himself%20was%20convinced%20that%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20was%20the%20right%20thing.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAshwin%20has%20exited%20the%20international%20stage%20in%20trademark%20style%2C%20ending%20a%20stellar%20career%20that%20many%20would%20have%20thought%20still%20had%20a%20few%20miles%20left%20in%20it.%20He%20is%20back%20in%20Chennai%20and%20looking%20forward%20to%20club%20cricket%2C%20including%20playing%20again%20for%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20in%20the%20IPL%20after%20almost%20a%20decade.%20He%20earlier%20spoke%20about%20how%20what%20impressed%20him%20most%20was%20the%20way%20CSK%20fought%20for%20him%20at%20the%20auction%2C%20something%20he%20didn't%20find%20in%20the%20Indian%20camp%20anymore.%20No%20one%20was%20fighting%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734612480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fv7an3ggo_r-ashwin_625x300_19_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fr-ashwin-the-one-that-got-away-7285644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20earlier%20spoke%20about%20how%20what%20impressed%20him%20most%20was%20the%20way%20CSK%20fought%20for%20him%20at%20the%20auction%2C%20something%20he%20didnt%20find%20in%20the%20Indian%20camp%20anymore.%20No%20one