nsider.com%2F676401c96c531c315b8932f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-fed-interest-rates-analyst-reaction-wall-street-stocks-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Federal%20Reserve%20cut%20interest%20rates%20on%20Wednesday%20but%20only%20projected%20two%20further%20cuts%20next%20year.%20Here's%20what%20analysts%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20news.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-fed-interest-rates-analyst-reaction-wall-street-stocks-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Man%20Among%208%20Arrested%20For%20Plan%20To%20Target%20RSS%2C%20Hindu%20Groups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20terrorist%20from%20Bangladesh%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20an%20Al-Qaeda%20affiliate%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20was%20among%20eight%20terrorists%20arrested%20by%20the%20Assam%20Police's%20Special%20Task%20Force%20(STF)%20from%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20national%20Md%20Sad%20Radi%20aka%20Md%20Shab%20Seikh%2C%2032%2C%20came%20to%20India%20in%20November%20to%20activate%20sleeper%20cells%20in%20Assam%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20before%20he%20moved%20to%20Kerala%2C%20the%20STF%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STF%20said%20they%20worked%20with%20the%20police%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengal%2C%20and%20launched%20'Operation%20Praghat'%20with%20reach%20across%20India%20after%20taking%20a%20detailed%20look%20into%20intelligence%20reports%20that%20a%20group%20of%20terrorists%20working%20under%20Md%20Farhan%20Israk%2C%20an%20aide%20of%20an%20Al%20Qaeda-affiliate%20leader%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20would%20try%20to%20activate%20sleeper%20cells%20in%20India%20to%20target%20members%20of%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20other%20Hindu%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMd%20Farhan%20Israk%20is%20very%20close%20to%20Jasimuddin%20Rahmani%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Ansarullah%20Bangla%20Team%2C%20an%20affiliate%20of%20the%20global%20terror%20group%20Al-Qaeda%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20the%20STF%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20major%20move%20against%20jihadi%20elements.%20The%20fact%20that%20we%20could%20nip%20this%20in%20the%20bud%20with%20the%20help%20of%20central%20agencies%2C%20and%20with%20the%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%20Police.%20I'd%20call%20it%20a%20success%20when%20we%20get%20more.%20But%20yes%2C%20we%20have%20made%20a%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20Assam%20Special%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%20Harmeet%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20apprehensions%20that%20were%20there%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20many%20regarding%20the%20situation%20emanating%20out%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20various%20parts%20of%20our%20western%20neighbour%20to%20destabilise%20our%20country%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20make%20a%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20yes%2C%20you%20could%20call%20it%20a%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMd%20Sad%20Radi%20met%20sleeper%20cells%20of%20the%20banned%20organisation%20Ansarullah%20Bangla%20Team%20(ABT)%20in%20Assam%20and%20Bengal%20before%20he%20headed%20to%20Kerala%20to%20contact%20more%20sleeper%20cells%2C%20the%20STF%20said%2C%20adding%20its%20chief%20and%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20Partha%20Sarathi%20Mahanta%20led%20teams%20across%20across%20the%20country%20to%20arrest%20the%20terror%20suspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STF%20arrested%20the%20eight%20suspects%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20December%2017-18%20during%20raids%20conducted%20simultaneously%20in%20Kerala%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20arrests%20prove%20the%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Bang