he%20confidence%26quot%3B%20China%20has%20in%20Russia%2C%20said%20Putin.%20He%20described%20China's%20leader%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20as%20his%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20how%20Russia%20fought%20alongside%20Chinese%20forces%20during%20World%20War%20II%20against%20Japan%20invaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20stood%20side%20by%20side%20with%20China%20then%20and%20we%20stand%20side%20by%20side%20them%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXi%20has%20spoken%20similarly%20warmly%20of%20Putin.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-bromance-xi-jinping-display-china-remains-wary-russia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeneath%20the%20bromance%20vibes%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20are%20significant%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20provided%20key%20diplomatic%20and%20economic%20support%20to%20Russia%20in%20its%20Ukraine%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20analysts%20say%20Putin%20likely%20resents%20being%20a%20junior%20partner%20to%20Xi%2C%20which%20vastly%20outstrips%20Russia%20in%20its%20population%20and%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-telling-moments-from-putins-marathon-end-of-year-event-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734609505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6763fbf3b1d5f0276b36da4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-telling-moments-from-putins-marathon-end-of-year-event-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Russian%20president%20addressed%20the%20faltering%20Russian%20economy%2C%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20the%20impending%20Trump%20administration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-telling-moments-from-putins-marathon-end-of