ement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnancy-mace-slams-woke-nonsense-points-out-redefinition-of-criminal-terms-in-cr%2Farticleshow%2F116465399.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnancy-mace-slams-woke-nonsense-points-out-redefinition-of-criminal-terms-in-cr%2Famp_articleshow%2F116465399.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnancy-mace-slams-woke-nonsense-points-out-redefinition-of-criminal-terms-in-cr%2Famp_articleshow%2F116465399.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Champions%20Trophy%20Venue%20Out%20But%20India%20Pay%20Big%20Price%20Due%20To%20ICC%20'Compromise'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20confusion%20surrounding%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20over.%20After%20months%20of%20delay%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20finally%20officially%20declared%20the%20venues%20for%20the%20elite%20event.%20%26quot%3BICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20to%20be%20played%20across%20Pakistan%20and%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20It%20means%20India%20will%20play%20its%20matches%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20including%20the%20knockout%20games%20(if%20it%20qualifies).%20In%20another%20major%20decision%2C%20the%20Jay%20Shah-led%20world%20body%20has%20declared%20that%20all%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20cricket%20matches%20in%20ICC%20events%2C%20hosted%20by%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20will%20be%20played%20at%20neutral%20venues%20till%202027.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20matches%20hosted%20by%20either%20country%20at%20ICC%20Events%20during%20the%202024-2027%20rights%20cycle%20will%20be%20played%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20the%20ICC%20Board%20confirmed%20on%20Thursday%2C%2019%20December%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20apply%20to%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20(hosted%20by%20Pakistan)%2C%20set%20to%20be%20played%20in%20February%20and%20March%202025%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202025%20(hosted%20by%20India)%20and%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202026%20(hosted%20by%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'compromise'%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20ICC%20means%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20will%20have%20to%20move%20out%20from%20its%20own%20country%20to%20play%20Pakistan%20in%20an%20ICC%20event%2C%20despite%20being%20the%20host%20or%20co-host.%20For%20a%20country%20that%20boasts%20itself%20to%20be%20a%20cricket%20power-house%2C%20that%20might%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20played%20each%20other%20only%20in%20ICC%20or%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20events%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20now.%20In%20this%20duration%2C%20whenever%20Pakistan%20has%20hosted%20an%20ICC%20or%20ACC%20event%2C%20India%20did%20not%20travel%20to%20the%20country%20and%20played%20its%20matches%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20last%20toured%20Pakistan%20for%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%202005-06.%20Pakistan%20last%20toured%20India%20for%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%202012-13.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20long%20impasse%20surrounding%20the%20hosting%20venue%20of%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20problem%20started%20after%20the%20BCCI%20said%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20sending%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20designated%20hosts%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20upon%20not%20receiving%20any%20clearance%20from%20the%20Indian%20government.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20then%20fumed%20and%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20a%20hybrid%20model%20of%20hosting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20they%20said%20that%20the%20same%20'hybrid%20model'%20would%20have%20to%20be%20adopted%20when%20India%20hosts%20an%20ICC%20event.%C2%A0%C2%A0It%20took%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come%20to%20the%20compromise%2C%20but%20now%20a%20middle-ground%20has%20been%20reached.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20also%20awarded%20the%C2%A0ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202028%20hosting%20rights%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20PCB%20has%20been%20awarded%20hosting%20rights%20of%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202028%2C%20where%20neutral%20venue%20arrangements%20will%20also%20apply.%20Cricket%20Australia%20is%20set%20to%20host%20one%20of%20the%20senior%20ICC%20women's%20events%20during%20the%20period%202029%20to%202031%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20schedule%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20set%20to%20be%20confirmed%20soon%2C%20with%20Pakistan%20aiming%20to%20defend%20the%20title%20they%20won%20in%202017.%20The%20eight-team%20event%20will%20feature%20Afghanistan%2C%20Australia%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20England%2C%20India%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20alongside%20hosts%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734608220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fi9tnj388_rohit-babar_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fchampions-trophy-2025-to-be-played-across-pakistan-and-a-neutral-venue-confirms-icc-7285255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20months%20of%20delay%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20finally%20officially%20declared%20the%20venues%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fchampions-trophy-2025-to-be-played-across-pakistan-and-a-neutral-venue-confirms-icc-7285255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20Auditor%20Confirms%20NDTV's%20Findings%20On%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Ration%20'Scam'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20NDTV%20exposed%20a%20shocking%20scandal%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20It%20was%20not%20just%20about%20money%20but%20also%20about%20the%20stolen%20future%20of%20children%2C%20pregnant%20women%20and%20adolescents%2C%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20government's%20nutrition%20scheme.%20The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20had%20dismissed%20the%20findings%20in%20the%20draft%20report%20but%20two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20confirmed%20the%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20confirmed%20that%20between%202018%20and%202021%2C%20a%20Rs%20428%20crore%20scam%20unravelled%20within%20the%20Take%20Home%20Ration%20(THR)%20scheme%2C%20which%20involved%20fake%20beneficiaries%2C%20fraudulent%20transportation%20claims%2C%20and%20corruption%20seeped%20into%20every%20layer%20of%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20NDTV%20Report%20Found%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFake%20Trucks%3A%20Trucks%20carrying%20nutrition%20rations%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20motorcycles%2C%20autos%2C%20and%20tankers.%20The%20CAG%20later%20verified%20that%20over%20400%20metric%20tons%20were%20never%20transported%20as%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhuge-corruption-in-madhya-pradesh-childrens-scheme-finds-state-auditor-3314883%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20Massive%20Scam%20On%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister's%20Watch%2C%20Finds%20Auditor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalse%20Numbers%3A%20The%20number%20of%20adolescent%20girls%20eligible%20for%20rations%20was%20inflated%20from%209%2C000%20to%20over%2036%20lakh%2C%20leading%20to%20Rs%20110%20crore%20being%20siphoned%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsc4cuki8_ndtv-report_625x300_19_December_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnreachable%20Food%3A%20While%20over%2096%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20ration%20were%20taken%20in%20stock%2C%20only%2086%2C000%20metric%20tons%20ever%20reached%20Anganwadi%20centres%2C%20leaving%20over%2010%2C000%20metric%20tons%20untraceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-food-scam-silent-on-malnutrition-chief-minister-shivraj-chouhan-cites-draft-report-3327589%5C%22%3EThese%20revelations%20caused%20a%20massive%20uproar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20While%20opposition%20leaders%20demanded%20accountability%2C%20the%20government%20scrambled%20to%20downplay%20the%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20CAG%20Report%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20echoed%20NDTV's%20findings.%20The%20report%20said%20Rs%2062.53%20crore%20worth%20of%20rations%20never%20reached%20their%20destinations.%20Nutrition%20samples%20worth%20Rs%20237%20crore%20failed%20quality%20checks%2C%20meaning%20beneficiaries%20likely%20received%20substandard%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F64gd1iuo_ndtv-report_625x300_19_December_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChild%20Development%20Project%20Officers%20(CDPOs)%20did%20not%20inspect%20Anganwadi%20centres%2C%20demonstrating%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20in%20oversight%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20finds%20itself%20under%20fire%20as%20political%20leaders%20demand%20accountability.%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister%20Sachin%20Yadav%20has%20called%20for%20immediate%20action%2C%20urging%20the%20government%20to%20investigate%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNDTV%20had%20exposed%20how%20the%20government's%20corruption%20snatched%20food%20from%20children%20and%20pregnant%20women.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20government%20dismissed%20the%20claims%2C%20but%20now%20even%20the%20CAG%20has%20confirmed%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Ba%20government%20of%20scams%2C%26quot%3B%20stating%20that%20public%20funds%20are%20being%20misused%20while%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20are%20left%20to%20suffer.%20Mr%20Yadav%20demanded%20strict%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20Rs%20428%20crore%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scam%20has%20ignited%20a%20war%20of%20words%20between%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20opposition.%20Minister%20Govind%20Singh%20Rajput%20dismissed%20the%20Congress's%20allegations%20as%20baseless%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20tell%20Congress%20that%20they%20lack%20real%20issues.%20Whatever%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20it%20will%20come%20out%20after%20an%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jaivardhan%20Singh%2C%20another%20Congress%20leader%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongratulations%20to%20NDTV%20for%20raising%20this%20issue%20prominently%20two%20years%20ago.%20We%20had%20said%20then%20that%20the%20government%20is%20robbing%20the%20poor%20of%20their%20rights.%20Now%20the%20names%20of%20all%20those%20involved%20in%20this%20scam%20must%20be%20revealed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmala%20Bhuria%2C%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Department%20Minister%2C%20appeared%20unaware%20of%20the%20scandal's%20details.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ar