y%20of%20origin's%20celebrations%20were%20orderly.%20Yes%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-10-shares-surprising-things-about-a-big-family-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elarger%20family%20gatherings%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20sometimes%20devolved%20into%20wrapping%20paper%20wars%20in%20a%20living%20room%20crammed%20way%20beyond%20fire%20code%20capacity.%20But%20that%20happened%20only%20after%20the%20well-organized%20gift%20opening.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20family%2C%20Christmas%20revolved%20around%20our%20fresh-cut%20tree%2C%20its%20pine%20scent%20filling%20the%20room%20as%20we%20opened%20gifts%20in%20an%20orderly%20fashion.%20Starting%20with%20the%20youngest%2C%20each%20person%20unwrapped%20one%20present%20at%20a%20time%2C%20allowing%20for%20collective%20admiration%20and%20expressed%20appreciation.%20The%20day%20unfolded%20with%20quiet%20rhythms%20%E2%80%94%20Bing%20Crosby%20on%20the%20record%20player%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-original-christmas-movies-ranked-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20movies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20TV%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20enjoy%20our%20gifts%20and%20each%20other's%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20I%20was%20sure%2C%20was%20the%20proper%20way%20to%20celebrate%20Christmas%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20my%20shock%2C%20then%2C%20when%20I%20attended%20my%20first%20Christmas%20gathering%20at%20my%20husband's%20house%2C%20ready%20for%20an%20orderly%20unwrapping%2C%20only%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20gift-opening%20melee.%20Everyone%20took%20their%20pile%20of%20gifts%20and%2C%20without%20fanfare%2C%20opened%20them%20all%20at%20once.%20There%20were%20no%20turns.%20There%20was%20no%20collective%20gasping%2C%20no%20posing%20for%20photos%20with%20my%20new%20sweater%20so%20Grandma%20could%20see%20how%20much%20I%20loved%20it%2C%20no%20feigned%20%26quot%3Bthank%20yous%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20really%20%3Cem%3Edidn't%3C%2Fem%3E%20love%20the%20new%20sweater.%20Instead%2C%20every%20gift%20in%20the%20entire%20room%20was%20unwrapped%20unceremoniously%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20less%20than%20two%20minutes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDid%20my%20new%20mother-in-law%20like%20the%20pink%20Angora%20sweater%20I%20gave%20her%3F%20How%20did%20my%20father-in-law%20feel%20about%20his%20work%20gloves%3F%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20because%20their%20reactions%20were%20lost%20under%20the%20wrapping%20paper.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20chaotic%20scene%20unfolded%20in%20front%20of%20an%20artificial%20tree%20that%20had%20become%20permanent%20in%20their%20dining%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20wild%20unwrapping%20and%20a%20shared%20meal%2C%20everyone%20put%20on%20coats%20and%20prepared%20to%20head%20outside.%20It%20was%20time%20for%20the%20next%20holiday%20tradition%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20movie%20theater.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20could%20count%20on%20one%20hand%20the%20number%20of%20times%20I%20had%20been%20to%20the%20movies%20with%20my%20family%2C%20and%20we%20never%20went%20on%20a%20holiday.%20That%20was%20sacrilegious.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20correct%20to%20celebrate%20Christmas%3B%20this%20Missouri%20version%20wasn't%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaised%20to%20be%20%26quot%3BIowa%20Nice%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20didn't%20say%20a%20word%20about%20my%20disapproval%2C%20but%20my%20facial%20expressions%20said%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a624c531-6943-4de7-8e07-b6632d6619f6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20adopted%202%20kids%2C%20we%20did%20the%20holidays%20our%20way%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20a%20few%20years%20into%20our%20marriage%2C%20those%20%26quot%3Bbabies%26quot%3B%20finally%20arrived%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%207%20and%208-year-old%20sons%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20adopted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20first%20Christmas%2C%20we%20worked%20hard%20not%20to%20overwhelm%20our%20children.%20Born%20in%20Ethiopia%2C%20they%20weren't%20used%20to%20the%20overstimulation%20that%20comes%20with%20large%20family%20gatherings.%20We%20kept%20the%20celebration%20simple%20and%20small%2C%20paring%20down%20the%20menu%2C%20the%20number%20of%20gifts%2C%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20gatherings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20felt%20good.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20simpler%2C%20quiet%20rhythms%20of%20the%20season%20allowed%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20really%20mattered.%20The%20four%20of%20us%20created%20new%20traditions%20that%20evolved%20over%20time.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20roasted%20a%20turkey%2C%20and%20other%20times%2C%20we%20dined%20on%20delicious%20Ethiopian%20food.%20Some%20years%2C%20we%20binged%20NBA%20games%20after%20opening%20gifts%2C%20and%20other%20years%2C%20we'd%20laugh%20at%20but%20secretly%20enjoy%20Hallmark%20movies.%20Maybe%20we'd%20play%20a%20game%2C%20or%20maybe%20we'd%20hop%20in%20the%20car%20to%20look%20at%20Christmas%20lights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20my%20parents%2C%20gifts%20are%20opened%20in%20turn%3B%20at%20my%20mother-in-law's%2C%20it's%20a%20fun-spirited%20free-for-all.%20My%20sons%20appreciate%20that%20there%20is%20no%20expectation%20to%20have%20the%20just-right%20reaction%20to%20packages%20of%20socks%20and%20underwear.%20Together%2C%20we've%20learned%20about%20flexibility%20and%20fluidity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20turns%20out%20there's%20no%20formula%20for%20the%20perfect%20holiday%2C%20even%20if%20I'm%20still%20not%20willing%20to%20budge%20on%20the%20fresh-cut%20tree.%20The%20magic%20of%20the%20holidays%20isn't%20in%20the%20tree%2C%20the%20gifts%2C%20or%20even%20the%20order%20of%20opening%20them%3B%20it's%20in%20embracing%20the%20p