%2C%20for%20the%20random%2C%20attempted%20slashing%20murder%20of%20a%20French%20tourist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Carro%20presided%20over%20the%20trial%20of%20an%20NYPD%20officer%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%20young%20fashion%20executive%20%E2%80%94%20a%20woman%20he'd%20been%20dispatched%20to%20help%20when%20she%20was%20too%20intoxicated%20to%20get%20out%20of%20her%20taxi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20cleared%20the%20officer%20of%20rape%20and%20convicted%20him%20of%20official%20misconduct%20for%20the%20three%20caught-on-video%20visits%20he%20made%20to%20the%20woman's%20apartment%20during%20his%20shift%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20misconduct%20offenses%20%26quot%3Brip%20at%20that%20fabric%20that%20holds%20us%20all%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Carro%20told%20the%20former%20officer%2C%20Kenneth%20Moreno%2C%20before%20sentencing%20him%20to%20a%20year%20at%20Rikers%20Island%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%2C%20sir%2C%20ripped%20a%20gaping%20hole%20in%20that%20fabric%20in%20committing%20those%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Carro's%20biggest%20media%20case%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreno's%20lawyer%2C%20Joe%20Tacopina%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20to%20call%20Carro%20%26quot%3Bno%20nonsense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20easy%20on%20defendants%20or%20defense%20lawyers%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Tacopina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20judge%20has%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20criminal%20attorney%20for%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20such%20overwhelming%20evidence%20of%20guilt%20here.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20'Who%20done%20it.'%20It%20is%20a%20'Was%20he%20sane%20when%20he%20did%20it'%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FILE%20PHOTO%3A%20Yoselyn%20Ortega%2C%20a%20nanny%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20killing%20Lucia%20and%20Leo%20Krim%2C%20ages%206%20and%202%20r