%2C%2060%2C%20admitted%20to%20running%20the%20secret%20station%20under%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China's%20(PRC)%20Ministry%20of%20Public%20Security%20(MPS).%20He%20faces%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20jail%20after%20pleading%20guilty%20to%20acting%20illegally%20as%20a%20foreign%20agent.%20His%20co-defendant%2C%20Lu%20Jianwang%2C%2062%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20US%20citizen%2C%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges%20and%20is%20awaiting%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20station%20was%20exposed%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20to%20disrupt%20Chinese%20government%20activities%20aimed%20at%20repressing%20Chinese-American%20pro-democracy%20activists.%20According%20to%20US%20Attorney%20Breon%20Peace%2C%20the%20operation%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Btransnational%20repression%20scheme%26quot%3B%20orchestrated%20by%20China%20to%20suppress%20dissent%20among%20its%20diaspora%20communities%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20station%20performed%20basic%20administrative%20functions%2C%20such%20as%20renewing%20Chinese%20driving%20licences%2C%20but%20also%20engaged%20in%20more%20%26quot%3Bsinister%26quot%3B%20activities%2C%20including%20helping%20locate%20a%20Chinese-American%20pro-democracy%20activist%20in%20California.%20FBI%20Assistant%20Director%20James%20Dennehy%20said%20Chen%20admitted%20his%20role%20in%20establishing%20the%20station%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bfurthered%20the%20repressive%20aims%20of%20the%20PRC%26quot%3B%20in%20violation%20of%20US%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20station%2C%20shut%20down%20in%20late%202022%2C%20was%20located%20on%20a%20whole%20floor%20of%20an%20office%20building%20in%20Manhattan's%20Chinatown.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20the%20FBI%20raided%20the%20facility%20and%20seized%20the%20phones%20of%20Chen%20and%20Lu.%20An%20investigation%20into%20the%20devices%20showed%20that%20messages%20between%20the%20two%20men%20and%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Public%20Security%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20erased.%20Chen's%20sentencing%20is%20scheduled%20for%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20been%20increasingly%20vigilant%20about%20foreign%20interference%2C%20with%20past%20cases%20involving%20attempts%20to%20influence%20US%20policies%20or%20pressure%20Chinese%20nationals%20living%20in%20the%20country.%20In%202020%2C%20many%20people%20were%20charged%20for%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20China%20to%20coerce%20a%20New%20Jersey%20man%20into%20returning%20to%20China.%20In%20September%202024%2C%20the%20US%20charged%20Linda%20Sun%2C%20a%20former%20aide%20to%20New%20York%20Governor%20Kathy%20Hochul%2C%20for%20covertly%20serving%20as%20an%20agent%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734600300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F6nrnd8go_new-york-city-_625x300_14_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecret-chinese-police-station-in-new-york-heres-the-real-story-7283292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chen%20Jinping%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20operating%20the%20secret%20police%20station%20for%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Public%20Security%20and%20faces%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20acting%20as%20an%20illegal%20foreign%20agent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecret-chinese-police-station-in-new-york-heres-the-real-story-7283292%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20impact%20of%20Swiss%20withdrawal%20of%20MFN%20status%20to%20country%3A%20Nestle%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734599942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fno-impact-of-swiss-withdrawal-of-mfn-status-to-country-nestle-india-124121900559_1.html%22%2C%22